{"tid":1743397,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警告：強光 - 所有攝影器材內 CMOS/CCD 的殺手","createTime":"2019-11-21T07:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T07:38:59.000Z","uid":293779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"317947f4541a5181cb117f6146c517d5ea04868c","tid":1743397,"uid":293779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"試過有一段日子用 單反拍攝日出，鏡頭是直指向太陽，有次的光線頗強，相信是感光組件受損，結果相機作廢！<br />\n<br />\n睇新聞片段，記者鏡頭被強光電筒照射下，不能清晰拍攝現場情況。<br />\n<br />\n智利近期發生的個案，警方用航拍機進行高空拍攝期間，多束鐳射光照向航拍機，據報導，航拍機鏡頭失明或機內感應器受影響，須要急降。<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/11/16/chile-protestors-use-laser-pointer-to-attack-police-drone/life-tech/drone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F11%2F16%2Fchile-protestors-use-laser-pointer-to-attack-police-drone%2Flife-tech%2Fdrone%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=aec5fe19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/11/16/chile-protestors-use-laser-pointer-to-attack-police-drone/life-tech/drone/</a><br />\n<br />\n同道理，「閉路電視」 的鏡頭內攝影組件，主要都是 CMOS/CCD，就算不被大力撞擊或塗抹，長時間受強光照射（如鐳射光/高能量電筒），也不能正常拍攝，甚至永久受損。<br />\n但「閉路電視」未受照射前，仍有可能拍攝到強光的來源 ! <br />\n不要用 道路攝錄鏡頭或智能燈柱做實驗，可能會被追究。<br />\n<br />\n未經進一步實驗測試，但請好好保護拍攝鏡頭，避免受強光長時間照射！<br />\n<br />\n温馨提示：<br />\n自拍/被拍時，請勿使用頭燈或 發光LED 頭飾，會影響拍攝效果。"},{"pid":"faf269eb68e22ac3c6e585d80c36a468de95d944","tid":1743397,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55500e320bfdec855b0425ebd7a1fc95dbafcb0","tid":1743397,"uid":41759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好用觀星筆直射鏡頭，sensor會壞架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4978fcab355eab621a941982eac92192f983ed2d","tid":1743397,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}